main event: A witness reported seeing a small round object changing colors from red to white over Phillips, Wisconsin, on 24 October 1957.
interesting points: The object was described as being the size of a basketball., The observation lasted for 5 minutes., The object moved in an up and down motion at angles., There were no photographs included in the report., The report concluded that there was insufficient data for analysis.
sighted object: small round object changing colors from red to white
